;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">My name&rsquo;s Mayumi Kimura and I&rsquo;m a student.</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">I&rsquo;m 19 years old.</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">I&rsquo;m not married.</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">I have two brothers and a sister.</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">I live in a flat in Osaka, Japan.</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">I want to learn English because it&rsquo;s an international language.</span></p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">Dialog 4.</p>\r\n<div id="mediaplayer4_wrapper" style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; position: relative; width: 300px; height: 24px;"><object id="mediaplayer4" width="100%" height="100%" name="mediaplayer4" bgcolor="#000000" data="http://www.tienganh123.com/jwplayer/