3; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">Fine, thank you. And you?</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;" /> <span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">A:&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">I&rsquo;m OK, thanks.</span></p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">Dialog 6.</p>\r\n<div id="mediaplayer6_wrapper" style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; position: relative; width: 300px; height: 24px;"><object id="mediaplayer6" width="100%" height="100%" name="mediaplayer6" bgcolor="#000000" data="http://www.tienganh123.com/jwplayer/player.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash"><param name="src" value="http://www.tienganh123.com/jwplayer/player.swf" /></object></div>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id="translate_6" style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;"><input id="translate_button" type="button" value="Xem b&agrave;i dịch" /></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id="show_mes_6" style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">A:&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">Hi, Dave. How are you?</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;" /> <span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">B:&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">Not bad, thanks. And you?</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;" /> <span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">A:&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">Very well. How are the children?</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;" /> <span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">B:&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">They&rsquo;re fine.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">Dialog 7.</p>\r\n<div id="mediaplayer7_wrapper" style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; position: relative; width: 300px; height: 24px;"><object id="mediaplayer7" width="100%" height="100%" name="mediaplayer7" bgcolor="#000000" data="http://www.tienganh123.com/jwplayer/player.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash"><param name="src" value="http://www.tienganh123.com/jwplayer/player.swf" /></object></div>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id="translate_7" style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;"><input id="translate_button" type="button" value="Xem b&agrave;i dịch" /></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id="show_mes_7" style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">A:&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">Goodbye, Chris.</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;" /> <span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">B:&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">Goodbye, Anne. Have a nice evening.</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;" /> <span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">A:&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">Thanks, Chris. See you tomorrow.</span></p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: x-large;">Post-listening</span></p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;"><strong>1. Khi l&agrave;m quen với một người, ta thường giới thiệu t&ecirc;n v&agrave; m&igrave;nh đến từ đ&acirc;u.</strong><br /> Eg.&nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;- &nbsp;My name&rsquo;s Jenny.&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span>&nbsp;<br /> -&nbsp;I&rsquo;m from New York.&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span>&nbsp;<br /> Cũng c&oacute; khi cũng c&ugrave;ng một th&ocirc;ng tin như thế, nhưng khi được hỏi,ta cũng c&oacute; thể trả lời ngắn gọn hơn l&agrave; &ldquo;Jenny&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;"><strong>2. Tự giới thiệu về bản th&acirc;n</strong><br /> Ta sẽ tự giới thiệu t&ecirc;n, tuổi, nghề nghiệp, v&agrave; c&oacute; thể n&oacute;i qua về gia đ&igrave;nh m&igrave;nh nữa.<br /> Ch&uacute; &yacute;: Động từ trong c&aacute;c c&acirc;u n&agrave;y thường ở th&igrave; hiện tại đơn.<br /> -&nbsp;I am a student.&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;"><strong>3. Khi gặp gỡ người quen, ta sẽ ch&agrave;o v&agrave; hỏi thăm như sau:</strong><br /> -&nbsp;Hi, Dave. How are you?&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span>&nbsp;<br /> Khi đ&atilde; th&acirc;n quen, người ta c&oacute; thể ch&agrave;o l&agrave; &ldquo;Hi&rdquo; thay v&igrave; &ldquo;Hello&rdquo; v&agrave; hỏi &ldquo;How are you?&rdquo;, người được hỏi sẽ trả lời l&agrave; &ldquo;fine&rdquo; hoặc &ldquo;not bad&rdquo;, c&aacute;m ơn v&agrave; hỏi lại, như thế n&agrave;y:<br /> -&nbsp;Fine, thank you. And you?&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;"><strong>4. Khi tạm biệt, ta sẽ ch&agrave;o &ldquo;goodbye&rdquo; v&agrave; hẹn gặp lại.</strong><br /> E.g.&nbsp;See you tomorrow.&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> See you again.&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: x-large;">B&agrave;i tập: Nghe lại v&agrave; điền từ v&agrave;o &ocirc; trống</span>&nbsp;(C&aacute;c bạn nghe v&agrave; điền hết 7 hội thoại v&agrave; c&oacute; n&uacute;t Check ở ph&ia