#333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">A:&nbsp;</span><input id="answer22" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; width: 7em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">, Chris.</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;" /> <span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">B: Goodbye, Anne. Have a nice&nbsp;</span><input id="answer23" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; width: 7em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">.</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;" /> <span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">A: Thanks, Chris.&nbsp;</span><input id="answer24" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; width: 3em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;you tomorrow.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;"><input type="button" value="Check" /></p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">Nghe b&agrave;i h&aacute;t sau v&agrave; điền c&aacute;c từ c&ograve;n thiếu v&agrave;o chỗ trống:</p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;"><a style="font-size: 10pt; color: #336699; text-decoration: none;" href="/06.WWW/index.php/sysadmin/content/"><span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;">B&agrave;i H&aacute;t - Click v&agrave;o đ&acirc;y!</span></a></p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;"><a style="font-size: 10pt; color: #336699; text-decoration: none;" href="/06.WWW/index.php/sysadmin/content/"><img src="http://data.tienganh123.com/file/baihoc/listening/beginner/listening_test.gif" alt="" border="0" /></a></p>', 'Bài đầu tiên, các bạn sẽ được học cách làm quen với một người lạ, giới thiệu về bản thân và chào hỏi một người đã quen biết.', 1, NULL, '2012-10-24 08:13:06', 195, 1, NULL, 8, '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `contents` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `excerpt`, `content`, `desc`, `premium`, `keywords`, `created_date`, `view`, `state`, `comment_status`, `category_id`, `video`, `translate`, `image`) VALUES
(18, 'Where do you come from? (Bạn đến từ đâu)', 'bai-2-where-do-you-come-from-ban-den-tu-dau', NULL, '<p><img style="display: none;" src="http://www.learnthailanguage.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/test-31.gif" alt="" width="200" height="150" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; padding: 5px 10px; line-height: 23px; float: left;">\r\n<p align="center"><strong><span style="font-size: x-large;">Where do you come from?</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: x-large;"><strong>Pre-listening</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-weight: bold;">1. Vocabulary</span></p>\r\n<table id="table1" style="width: 500px;" border="0" cellpadding="1" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="68">football</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">\r\n<h5><span style="font-family: ''Lucida Sans Unicode''; font-size: medium;"><span class="mw-headline"><span style="font-weight: 400;">/ˈfʊtˌbɔl/</span></span></span></h5>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="40">(n)</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="129"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="112">b&oacute;ng đ&aacute;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="68">vacation</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">\r\n<h5><span style="font-family: ''Lucida Sans Unicode''; font-size: medium;"><span class="mw-headline"><span style="font-weight: 400;">/və''kei&int;n/</span></span></span></h5>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="40">(n)</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="129"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="112">k&igrave; nghỉ</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="68">fun</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">\r\n<h5><span style="font-family: ''Lucida Sans Unicode''; font-size: medium;"><span class="mw-headline"><span style="font-weight: 400;">/fʌn/</span></span></span></h5>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="40">(n)</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="129"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="112">niềm vui</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="68">great</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">\r\n<h5><span style="font-family: ''Lucida Sans Unicode''; font-size: medium;"><span class="mw-headline"><span style="font-weight: 400;">/greɪt/</span></span></span></h5>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="40">(adj)</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="129"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="112">tuyệt vời</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="68">like</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">\r\n<h5><span style="font-family: ''Lucida Sans Unicode''; font-size: medium;"><span class="mw-headline"><span style="font-weight: 400;">/laik/</span></span></span></h5>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="40">(v)</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="129"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="112">th&iacute;ch</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="68" height="50">best</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" height="50">\r\n<h5><span style="font-family: ''Lucida Sans Unicode''; font-size: medium;"><span class="mw-headline"><span style="font-weight: 400;">/best/</span></span></span></h5>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="40" height="50">(adj)</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="129" height="50"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="112" height="50">tốt nhất, tuyệt nhất</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="68">kind</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">\r\n<h5><span style="font-family: ''Lucida Sans Unicode''; font-size: medium;"><span class="mw-headline"><span style="font-weight: 400;">/kaind/</span></span></span></h5>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="40">(adj)</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="129"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="112">tốt</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="68">spicy</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">\r\n<h5><span style="font-family: ''Lucida Sans Unicode''; font-size: medium;"><span class="mw-headline"><span style="font-weight: 400;">/&acute;spaisi/</span></span></span></h5>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="40">(adj)</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="129"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="112">cay</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="68" height="31">stay</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" height="31">\r\n<h5><span style="font-family: ''Lucida Sans Unicode''; font-size: medium;"><span class="mw-headline"><span style="font-weight: 400;">/stei/</span></span></span></h5>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="40" height="31">(v)</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="129" height="31"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="112" height="31">ở ( đ&acirc;u đ&oacute;)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="68">big</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">\r\n<h5><span style="font-family: ''Lucida Sans Unicode''; font-size: medium;"><span class="mw-headline"><span style="font-weight: 400;">/big/</span></span></span></h5>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="40">(adj)</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="129"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="112">lớn</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="68">work</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="font-family: ''Lucida Sans Unicode'';">/wɜ:k/</span></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="40">(v)</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="129"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="112">l&agrave;m việc</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="68">import</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">\r\n<h5><span style="font-family: ''Lucida Sans Unicode''; font-size: medium;"><span class="mw-headline"><span style="font-weight: 400;">/im&acute;pɔ:t/</span></span></span></h5>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="40">(v)</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="129"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="112">nhập khẩu</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="68">bank</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">\r\n<h5><span style="font-family: ''Lucida Sans Unicode''; font-size: medium;"><span class="mw-headline"><span style="font-weight: 400;">/b&aelig;&eta;k/</span></span></span></h5>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="40">(n)</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="129"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="112">ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="68">bank teller</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">\r\n<h5><span style="font-family: ''Lucida Sans Unicode''; font-size: medium;"><span class="mw-headline"><span style="font-weight: 400;">/b&aelig;&eta;k ''telə(r)/</span></span></span></h5>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="40">(n)</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="129"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="112">nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="68">owner</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">\r\n<h5><span style="font-family: ''Lucida Sans Unicode''; font-size: medium;"><span class="mw-headline"><span style="font-weight: 400;">/&acute;ounə/</span></span></span></h5>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="40">(n)</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="129"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="112">chủ</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="68">company</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">\r\n<h5><span style="font-family: ''Lucida Sans Unicode''; font-size: medium;"><span class="mw-headline"><span style="font-weight: 400;">/&acute;kʌmpəni/</span></span></span></h5>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="40">(n)</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="129"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="112">c&ocirc;ng ty</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>2. Brainstorm</strong><br /> Khi n&oacute;i chuyện với người mới quen, thường thường ta sẽ hỏi qu&ecirc; qu&aacute;n, sở th&iacute;ch v&agrave; c&ocirc;ng việc.<br /> &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="center"><img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/baihoc/listening/beginner/bai2/bai2_1.gif" alt="" width="450" height="294" border="0" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: x-large;">Listening</span></strong></p>\r\n<p align="center"><img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/baihoc/listening/beginner/bai2/bai2_2.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="299" border="0" /></p>\r\n<p>1. First time: Đoạn hội thoại sau l&agrave; cuộc n&oacute;i chuyện giữa hai người bạn mới quen, c&aacute;c bạn h&atilde;y ch&uacute; &yacute; nghe xem hai người đ&oacute; đang n&oacute;i g&igrave; nh&eacute;.</p>\r\n<div id="mediaplayer1_wrapper" style="position: relative; width: 300px; height: 24px;"><object id="mediaplayer1" width="100%" height="100%" name="mediaplayer1" bgcolor="#000000" data="http://www.tienganh123.com/jwplayer/player.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash"><param name="src" value="http://www.tienganh123.com/jwplayer/player.swf" /></object></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id="xemdich_1"><input id="xemdich_button_1" type="button" value="Xem b&agrave;i dịch" /></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div id="thongbao_1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong>* Transcript</strong></span>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>Hello.</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>Hello.</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>How are you?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>I''m fine, Thank you. And you?</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>I''m fine, thank you. Where are you from?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>I come from England.</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>You come from England! Do you like Manchester United?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>Um, I don''t like football.</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>Oh, You don''t like football, I see. Why did you come here?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>I came for vacation.</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>You came for vacation? Are you having fun?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>Yes, I''m having a great time.</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>What do you like best here?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>What do I like best? Well, the people are very kind.</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>Yes, the people here are kind. Do you like the food?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>Yes! The food is great!</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>Is the food too spicy for you?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>No, I love spicy food! I can eat spicy food everyday.</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;How much longer will you stay here?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:</strong>&nbsp;I will stay two more days.</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>Oh! Then you will go home?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>Yes, then I will go home.</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>Where do you work?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>I work for a big company.</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>What kind of company do you work for?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>I work for an import company. And what about you?</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>I work at a bank.</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>Uh. Are you a bank teller?</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>No, I''m the owner.</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>Oh.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>2. Second time:&nbsp;<a style="font-size: 10pt; color: #336699; text-decoration: none;" href="/06.WWW/index.php/sysadmin/content/"><span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: large;">Click v&agrave;o đ&acirc;y để nghe v&agrave; l&agrave;m b&agrave;i tập</span></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: x-large;"><strong>Post-listening</strong></span></p>\r\n<strong>1.&nbsp;</strong>Khi n&oacute;i chuyện với một người mới quen, bạn n&ecirc;n n&oacute;i đến những nội dung quen thuộc v&ocirc; thưởng v&ocirc; phạt ( v&iacute; như hỏi qu&ecirc; qu&aacute;n, sở th&iacute;ch, c&ocirc;ng việc)\r\n<p><strong>Eg.</strong>&nbsp;Where are you from?</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Do you like Manchester United?</p>\r\n<p><strong>2.&nbsp;</strong>C&oacute; một điều bạn phải đặc biệt lưu &yacute; khi giao tiếp với người lạ, nhất l&agrave; người phương T&acirc;y: kh&ocirc;ng hỏi tuổi, kh&ocirc;ng hỏi tiền lương hoặc những vấn đề ri&ecirc;ng tư kh&aacute;c.</p>\r\n<p>Eg. Tr&aacute;nh hỏi&nbsp;"How old are you?"</p>\r\n<p><strong>3.&nbsp;</strong>Vấn đề g&acirc;y kh&oacute; nghe chuẩn:&nbsp;<em><strong>Ph&aacute;t &acirc;m kh&ocirc;ng chuẩn</strong></em></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; t&igrave;nh huống rất phổ biến đối với mọi người khi học tiếng Anh. Nhiều l&uacute;c c&aacute;c bạn kh&ocirc;ng nghe r&otilde; v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng hiểu từ m&igrave;nh nghe được l&agrave; từ g&igrave;,nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n l&agrave; do ph&aacute;t &acirc;m kh&ocirc;ng ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c.</p>\r\n<p>Eg. Một số người vẫn thường ghi như thế n&agrave;y để nhớ c&aacute;ch ph&aacute;t &acirc;m:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/baihoc/listening/beginner/bai2/bai2_3.jpg" alt="" width="277" height="63" border="0" /></p>\r\n<p>nhưng điều n&agrave;y l&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng n&ecirc;n. N&oacute; sẽ l&agrave;m bạn ph&aacute;t &acirc;m sai v&agrave; c&agrave;ng học theo c&aacute;ch đ&oacute;, sau n&agrave;y bạn c&agrave;ng kh&oacute; sửa c&aacute;ch ph&aacute;t &acirc;m của m&igrave;nh cho ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c.</p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c bạn n&ecirc;n học theo bảng sau: (Tham khảo th&ecirc;m trong phần&nbsp;<a style="font-size: 10pt; color: #336699; text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.tienganh123.com/?c=mod-23" target="_blank"><em>b&agrave;i học - ph&aacute;t &acirc;m</em></a><a style="font-size: 10pt; color: #336699;">)</a></p>\r\n<p align="center"><a style="font-size: 10pt; color: #336699;"><img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/baihoc/listening/beginner/bai2/phonetics.gif" alt="" width="589" height="377" border="0" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-size: 10pt; color: #336699;">&nbsp;</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: x-large;">B&agrave;i tập: Nghe lại v&agrave; điền từ v&agrave;o &ocirc; trống</span></a></p>\r\n<div id="mediaplayer2_wrapper" style="position: relative; width: 300px; height: 24px;"><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><object id="mediaplayer2" width="100%" height="100%" name="mediaplayer2" bgcolor="#000000" data="http://www.tienganh123.com/jwplayer/player.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash"><param name="src" value="http://www.tienganh123.com/jwplayer/player.swf" /></object></a></div>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;Hello.</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>W:</strong>&nbsp;Hello.</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;<input id="answer0" style="width: 3em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;are you?</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>W:</strong>&nbsp;I''m&nbsp;<input id="answer1" style="width: 4em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />, Thank you. And you?</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;I''m fine, thank you. Where are you&nbsp;<input id="answer2" style="width: 4em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />?</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>W:</strong>&nbsp;I come from&nbsp;<input id="answer3" style="width: 7em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />.</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;You come from England! Do you&nbsp;<input id="answer4" style="width: 4em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;Manchester United?</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>W:</strong>&nbsp;Um, I don''t like&nbsp;<input id="answer5" style="width: 8em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />.</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;Oh, You don''t like football, I&nbsp;<input id="answer6" style="width: 3em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />. Why did you come&nbsp;<input id="answer7" style="width: 4em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />?</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>W:</strong>&nbsp;I came for&nbsp;<input id="answer8" style="width: 8em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />.</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;You came for vacation? Are you having&nbsp;<input id="answer9" style="width: 3em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />?</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>W:</strong>&nbsp;Yes, I''m having a&nbsp;<input id="answer10" style="width: 5em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;time.</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;What do you like&nbsp;<input id="answer11" style="width: 4em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;here?</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>W:</strong>&nbsp;What do I like best? Well, the people are very&nbsp;<input id="answer12" style="width: 4em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />.</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;Yes, the people here are kind. Do you like the&nbsp;<input id="answer13" style="width: 4em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />?</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>W:</strong>&nbsp;Yes! The food is great!</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;Is the food&nbsp;<input id="answer14" style="width: 3em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;spicy for you?</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>W:</strong>&nbsp;No, I love spicy food! I can eat spicy food&nbsp;<input id="answer15" style="width: 8em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />.</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;How much longer will you&nbsp;<input id="answer16" style="width: 4em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;here?</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>W:</strong>&nbsp;I will stay two more&nbsp;<input id="answer17" style="width: 4em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />.</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;Oh! Then you will go&nbsp;<input id="answer18" style="width: 4em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />?</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>W:</strong>&nbsp;Yes, then I will go home.</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;<input id="answer19" style="width: 5em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;do you work?</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>W:</strong>&nbsp;I work for a big company.</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;<input id="answer20" style="width: 4em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;kind of company do you work for?</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>W:</strong>&nbsp;I work for an&nbsp;<input id="answer21" style="width: 6em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;company. And&nbsp;<input id="answer22" style="width: 4em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;about you?</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;I work at a&nbsp;<input id="answer23" style="width: 4em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />.</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>W:</strong>&nbsp;Uh. Are you a bank teller?</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;No, I''m the&nbsp;<input id="answer24" style="width: 5em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />.</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>W:</strong>&nbsp;Oh.</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><input type="button" value="Check" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: x-large;">Nghe b&agrave;i h&aacute;t</span></a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>I Will Be Here(Steven Curtis Chapman)</strong></a></p>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt; color: #333333;" valign="top" width="400"><a style="font-family: Arial; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><object width="400" height="300" data="http://www.youtube.com/v/3X8U6am5iX4?fs=1&amp;hl=en_US" type="application/x-shockwave-flash"><param name="src" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/3X8U6am5iX4?fs=1&amp;hl=en_US" /><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /></object></a></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt; color: #333333;" valign="top" width="300">\r\n<div class="loibh" style="font-size: 12px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid #d9d9d9; height: 288px; line-height: 18px; overflow-y: scroll;">\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;">Tomorrow morning if you wake up&nbsp;<br /> and the sun does not appear<br /> I will be here<br /> If in the dark, we lose sight of love<br /> Hold my hand, and have no fear<br /> ''Cause I will be here<br /> <br /> I will be here<br /> When you feel like being quiet<br /> When you need to speak your mind<br /> I will listen<br /> And I will be here<br /> When the laughter turns to cryin''<br /> Through the winning, losing and trying<br /> We''ll be together<br /> I will be here<br /> <br /> Tomorrow morning, if you wake up<br /> And the future is unclear<br /> I will be here<br /> Just as sure as seasons were made for change<br /> Our lifetimes were made for these years<br /> So I will be here<br /> <br /> I will be here<br /> And you can cry on my shoulder<br /> When the mirror tells us we''re older<br /> I will hold you<br /> And I will be here<br /> To watch you grow in beauty<br /> And tell you all the things you are to me<br /> I will be here<br /> <br /> I will be true to the promise I have made<br /> To you and to the One who gave you to me<br /> <br /> Tomorrow morning, if you wake up<br /> And the sun does not appear<br /> I will be here<br /> Oh, I will be here.</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong><span style="font-size: large;">More Exercise</span></strong>&nbsp;(Nghe lại b&agrave;i h&aacute;t v&agrave; điền c&aacute;c từ c&ograve;n thiếu v&agrave;o chỗ trống)</a></p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20px;"><a style="font-size: 10pt; color: #336699; text-decoration: none;" href="/06.WWW/index.php/sysadmin/content/"><span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;">B&agrave;i H&aacute;t - Click v&agrave;o đ&acirc;y!</span></a></p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20px;"><img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/baihoc/listening/beginner/listening_test.gif" alt="" border="0" /></p>', 'Khi nói chuyện với người mới quen, thường thường ta sẽ hỏi quê quán, sở thích và công việc.', 0, NULL, '2012-10-24 08:15:05', 32, 1, NULL, 8, '', '', '');
