ng ta nghe mẩu hội thoại:<br /> <span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></h2>\r\n<div id="media">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><em>I''m&nbsp;</em>l&agrave; viết tắt của&nbsp;<em>I am</em>&nbsp;- đ&acirc;y l&agrave; động từ&nbsp;<em>"to be"</em>&nbsp;chia ở ng&ocirc;i thứ nhất số &iacute;t.\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id="translate"><input id="translate_button" type="button" value="Xem b&agrave;i dịch" /></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div id="show_mes">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div id="a"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/file/baihoc/streamlineA/bai1/1.1.PNG" alt="" width="118" height="140" align="left" border="0" />A:&nbsp;Hello!\r\n<p>B:&nbsp;Hello!&nbsp;<br /> A:&nbsp;I''m David Clark .</p>\r\n<p>B:&nbsp;I''m Linda Martin.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<br /> <img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/file/baihoc/streamlineA/bai1/1.2.PNG" alt="" width="109" height="130" align="left" border="0" />C:&nbsp;Are you a teacher?\r\n<p>D:&nbsp;No, I''m not.</p>\r\n<p>C:&nbsp;Oh, are you a student?</p>\r\n<p>D:&nbsp;Yes, I am.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="a"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/file/baihoc/streamlineA/bai1/1.3.PNG" alt="" width="118" height="140" align="left" border="0" />E:&nbsp;Are you from England?\r\n<p>F:&nbsp;&nbsp;No, I''m not.</p>\r\n<p>E:&nbsp;Where are you from?</p>\r\n<p>F:&nbsp;I''m from Canada.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/file/baihoc/streamlineA/bai1/1.4.PNG" alt="" width="118" height="140" align="left" border="0" />G:&nbsp;Hello, John!\r\n<p>H:&nbsp;Hello Peter. How are you?</p>\r\n<p>G:&nbsp;I''m very well, thanks. And you?</p>\r\n<p>H:&nbsp;I''m fine, thanks.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h2><br /> &nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table id="table12" style="width: 500px;" border="0" cellspacing="1">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;"><strong class="b1"><span style="font-size: 16pt;">Grammar - Ngữ Ph&aacute;p</span></strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">1. Personal Pronouns (Đại từ nh&acirc;n xưng)</span>\r\n<p>Đại từ nh&acirc;n xưng l&agrave; những từ d&ugrave;ng trong xưng h&ocirc; giao tiếp</p>\r\n<p>Trong tiếng Anh c&oacute; 3 ng&ocirc;i:</p>\r\n<table id="table13" style="width: 100%;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="72%"><strong>Ng&ocirc;i</strong></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="12%"><strong>Số &iacute;t</strong></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="16%"><strong>Số nhiều</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">Thứ 1 (Chỉ người n&oacute;i)</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">I</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">We</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">Thứ 2 (Chỉ người nghe)</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">You</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">You</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">Thứ 3&nbsp; (Được người n&oacute;i đề cập tới (kh&ocirc;ng tham gia trực tiếp v&agrave;o c&acirc;u chuyện)</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">He&nbsp;&nbsp;<br /> She&nbsp;&nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;It</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">They</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table id="table14" style="width: 100%;" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" colspan="2"><strong class="b1">Notes (Ch&uacute; &yacute;)</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" colspan="2">We với nghĩa "ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i" chỉ bao gồm những người n&oacute;i</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;"><em>E.g.&nbsp; Can we go out now?</em></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center"><em><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;"><em>Yes, you can.</em></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" colspan="2">We với nghĩa "ch&uacute;ng ta&nbsp; sẽ bao gồm cả người n&oacute;i lẫn người nghe.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;"><em>E.g.&nbsp; Can we go out now?<br /> &nbsp;</em></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center"><em><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;"><em>Yes, we can. Let''s go now.</em>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="color: #990000;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">2. The Present Simple Tense of "<strong>to be</strong>" (Th&igrave; hiện tại của động từ "<strong>to be</strong>")</span></p>\r\n<p>Động từ "to be" thường mang nghĩa l&agrave;: Th&igrave;, l&agrave;, bị, ở, được (lưu &yacute; chức năng ch&iacute;nh của động từ to be chỉ mang chức năng ngữ ph&aacute;p chứ kh&ocirc;ng phải l&agrave; ngữ nghĩa).&nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong class="b1">C&acirc;u khẳng định</strong></p>\r\n<table id="table15" style="width: 61%;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="70">I<br /> &nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="47">''m<br /> am</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" rowspan="5">&nbsp;&nbsp;<em>I am a student.<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></em>\r\n<p><br /> <br /> <em>She is from England.</em><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" rowspan="2" width="70">You</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="47">''re</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="47">are</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="70">He</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" rowspan="2" width="47">''s<br /> is</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="70">She</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<strong class="b1">C&acirc;u nghi vấn</strong>\r\n<p style="color: #990000; height: 27px; line-height: 27px;">Yes / No Questions.</p>\r\n<table id="table16" style="width: 60%;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="46">Am</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="44">I</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" rowspan="3">&nbsp;&nbsp;<em>&nbsp;Am I a student?<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></em>\r\n<p><br /> <br /> <em>Are you from England?</em><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="46" height="23">Are</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="44" height="23">you</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="46" height="42">Is</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="44" height="42">she<br /> he</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table id="table17" style="width: 39%;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" rowspan="4" width="16%">Yes,</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="31%">I am</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center" width="11%"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">you are</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">he is</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">she is</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" rowspan="6">No,</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">I''m not</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">I am not</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">You aren''t</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">You are not</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">He isn''t</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">She is not</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="color: #990000; height: 27px; line-height: 27px;"><strong><span style="font-size: medium;">C&acirc;u hỏi c&oacute; từ để hỏi</span></strong></p>\r\n<table id="table18" style="width: 359px;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">Where</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">am I<br /> are you<br /> is he<br /> is she</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">from?</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;"><em><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial;">&rarr;</span>&nbsp;I''m from Canada<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="color: #990000; height: 27px; line-height: 27px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">E.g.</span></p>\r\n<table id="table19" style="width: 100%;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="30%" height="26">- Where is she from?</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="40%"><em>C&ocirc; ấy đến từ đ&acirc;u?)</em></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center" width="30%"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" height="27">-She is from Italy</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;"><em>C&ocirc; ấy đến từ nước &Yacute;.</em></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">- She is Italian</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;"><em>C&ocirc; ấy l&agrave; người &Yacute;.</em></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p><br /> <strong class="b1">Trong b&agrave;i học h&ocirc;m nay c&oacute; một số từ mới v&agrave; mẫu c&acirc;u cần ghi nhớ:</strong></p>\r\n<table id="table20" style="width: 100%;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" colspan="2">Từ mới:&nbsp; Come, fine, thanks</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" colspan="2">Mẫu c&acirc;u:</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" width="70%" height="29">- How are you?</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center" width="30%"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" height="33">- Fine, thanks. And you?</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" height="28">- Fine, thanks.</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" height="27">- Where are you from?</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" height="30">- I''m from ...</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" height="29">- Are you from ....?</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" height="34">- Yes. I am.&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">- No. I am not.</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="menu_bot" style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.63636302947998px;">\r\n<div class="mnbot_left">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Bài 1 - Xin chào', 0, NULL, '2012-10-26 06:36:41', 2, 1, NULL, 23, '', '', ''),
(29, 'Joe Sabia: The technology of storytelling', 'joe-sabia-the-technology-of-storytelling', NULL, '<p><span><strong><img style="display: none;" src="http://www.tienganh123.com/file/video/TED/bai20/bai20.jpg" alt="" width="320" height="180" /></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><a title="Về t&aacute;c giả" href="javascript:void(0)"><span><strong>About the speaker</strong></span></a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Joe Sabia" href="javascript:void(0)"><span>Joe Sabia</span></a><br /><a title="Joe Sabia đ&atilde; kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; ra c&aacute;ch kể chuyện mới &ndash; kết hợp giữa video ph&acirc;n giải cao v&agrave; c&ocirc;ng nghệ hiển thị mới với c&acirc;u chuyện cổ." href="javascript:void(0)"><span>Joe Sabia investigates new ways to tell stories -- meshing viral video and new display technologies with old-fashioned narrative</span></a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Về b&agrave;i ph&aacute;t biểu" href="javascript:void(0)"><span><strong>About this talk</strong></span></a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Joe Sabia đ&atilde; kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; ra c&aacute;ch kể chuyện mới &ndash; kết hợp giữa video ph&acirc;n giải cao v&agrave; c&ocirc;ng nghệ hiển thị mới với c&acirc;u chuyện cổ." href="javascript:void(0)"><span>iPad storyteller Joe Sabia introduces us to Lothar Meggendorfer, who created a bold technology for storytelling: the pop-up book. Sabia shows how new technology has always helped us tell our own stories, from the walls of caves to his own onstage iPad.</span></a></p>', 'Joe Sabia: Công nghệ kể chuyện', 1, NULL, '2012-10-26 06:51:09', 167, 1, NULL, 24, '<p><span id="preview"><object id="player" width="400" height="300" data="/06.WWW/assets/40251131/plugins/media/moxieplayer.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash"><param name="src" value="/06.WWW/assets/40251131/plugins/media/moxieplayer.swf" /><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="true" /><param name="quality" value="high" /><param name="flashvars" value="url=/06.WWW/uploads/Video/hoc_qua_clip/ted.flv&amp;poster=/06.WWW/index.php/sysadmin/content/" /></object></span></p>\r\n<script type="mce-text/javascript" src="/includes/swfobject.js"></script>\r\n<script type="mce-text/javascript">// <![CDATA[\r\nvar s1 = new SWFObject("/includes/player.swf","player","400","300","9"); \r\n			s1.addParam("allowfullscreen","true"); \r\n			s1.addParam("allowscriptaccess","always"); \r\n			s1.addParam("flashvars","file=http://video.tienganh123.com/TED/bai20.flv&image=http://tienganh123.com/file/video/TED/bai20/bai20.jpg"); \r\n			s1.write("preview");\r\n// ]]></script>', '<p><a title="Joe Sabia: C&ocirc;ng nghệ kể chuyện" href="javscript:void(0)"><span><strong>Joe Sabia: The technology of storytelling</strong></span></a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Thưa qu&yacute; vị c&oacute; mặt h&ocirc;m nay. T&ocirc;i muốn chia sẻ với c&aacute;c bạn một c&acirc;u chuyện." href="javascript:void(0)"><span>Ladies and gentlemen, gather around. I would love to share with you a story.</span></a></p>\r\n<div id="non_paid_member_hide">\r\n<p><a title="Ng&agrave;y xửa ng&agrave;y xưa v&agrave;o hồi thế kỷ 19 ở nước Đức, c&oacute; một cuốn s&aacute;ch. Trong suốt thời gian đ&oacute;, s&aacute;ch ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; &ocirc;ng vua kể chuy&ecirc;̣n." href="javscript:void(0)">Once upon a time in 19th century Germany, there was the book. Now during this time, the book was the king of storytelling</a>.&nbsp;<a title="S&aacute;ch thật thi&ecirc;ng li&ecirc;ng. S&aacute;ch c&oacute; mặt ở khắp mọi nơi. Nhưng n&oacute; lại hơi nh&agrave;m ch&aacute;n." href="javascript:void(0)">It was venerable. It was ubiquitous. But it was a little bit boring</a>.<a title="Bởi v&igrave; trong suốt 400 năm tồn tại của m&igrave;nh, những người kể chuy&ecirc;̣n chẳng bao giờ ph&aacute;t triển s&aacute;ch để biến n&oacute; th&agrave;nh một thiết bị kể chuy&ecirc;̣n. Nhưng rồi c&oacute; một t&aacute;c giả xuất hiện v&agrave; &ocirc;ng ấy đ&atilde; thay đổi cục diện m&atilde;i m&atilde;i." href="javascript:void(0)">Because in its 400 years of existence, storytellers never evolved the book as a storytelling device. But then one author arrived, and he changed the game forever</a>.(Music)&nbsp;<a title="T&ecirc;n &ocirc;ng ấy l&agrave; Lothar, Lothar Meggendorfer. Lothar Meggendorfer đ&atilde; dậm ch&acirc;n, v&agrave; tuy&ecirc;n bố: &quot;Đủ nghĩa l&agrave; đủ!&quot;" href="javascript:void(0)">His name was Lothar, Lothar Meggendorfer. Lothar Meggendorfer put his foot down, and he said, "Genug ist genug!"</a><a title="&Ocirc;ng chộp lấy c&acirc;y b&uacute;t, v&agrave; vồ lấy c&aacute;i k&eacute;o. Người đ&agrave;n &ocirc;ng n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng tu&acirc;n theo c&aacute;c quy ước th&ocirc;ng thường v&agrave; quyết định l&agrave;m điều g&igrave; đ&oacute; kh&aacute;c biệt." href="javascript:void(0)">He grabbed his pen, he snatched his scissors. This man refused to fold to the conventions of normalcy and just decided to fold</a>.&nbsp;<a title="Lịch sử biết về Lothar Meggendorfer như l&agrave; -- ai kh&aacute;c nữa nhỉ? -- người đầu ti&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n thế giới ph&aacute;t minh s&aacute;ch động cho trẻ em. V&igrave; sự th&iacute;ch th&uacute;, v&agrave; sự kỳ diệu n&agrave;y, mọi người đều hoan hỷ. Họ hạnh ph&uacute;c v&igrave; c&acirc;u chuy&ecirc;̣n sẽ sống l&acirc;u hơn, v&agrave; rằng tr&aacute;i đất vẫn tiếp tục quay." href="javascript:void(0)">History would know Lothar Meggendorfer as -- who else? -- the world''s first true inventor of the children''s pop-up book. (Music)&nbsp;For this delight and for this wonder, people rejoiced. (Cheering) They were happy because the story survived, and that the world would keep on spinning.</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Lothar Meggendorfer kh&ocirc;ng phải l&agrave; người đầu ti&ecirc;n ph&aacute;t triển c&aacute;ch thức kể chuy&ecirc;̣n, v&agrave; chắc nhất định kh&ocirc;ng phải l&agrave; người cuối c&ugrave;ng. D&ugrave; những người kể chuy&ecirc;̣n c&oacute; nhận ra hay kh&ocirc;ng, họ đang nối tiếp tinh thần của Meggendorfer khi họ ph&aacute;t triển nhạc kịch th&agrave;nh đại nhạc hội, tin tức v&ocirc; tuyến th&agrave;nh rạp h&aacute;t v&ocirc; tuyến, phim chụp đến phim chuyển động rồi phim c&oacute; tiếng, phim m&agrave;u, phim 3D, tr&ecirc;n băng từ v&agrave; tr&ecirc;n DVD.  Dường như kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; c&aacute;ch g&igrave; chống lại ảnh-hưởng-Meggendorfer n&agrave;y. " href="javascript:void(0)"><span>Lothar Meggendorfer wasn''t the first to evolve the way a story was told, and he certainly wasn''t the last. Whether storytellers realized it or not, they were channeling Meggendorfer''s spirit when they moved opera to vaudville, radio news to radio theater, film to film in motion to film in sound, color, 3D, on VHS and on DVD.</span>&nbsp;There seemed to be no cure for this Meggendorferitis.</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Dường như kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; c&aacute;ch g&igrave; chống lại ảnh-hưởng-Meggendorfer n&agrave;y. V&iacute; dụ như, một c&ocirc;ng ty c&oacute; thể kể một c&acirc;u chuy&ecirc;̣n t&igrave;nh y&ecirc;u qua ch&iacute;nh bộ m&aacute;y t&igrave;m kiếm của m&igrave;nh. Một h&atilde;ng sản xuất phim Đ&agrave;i Loan c&oacute; thể m&ocirc; phỏng ch&iacute;nh trị Hoa Kỳ bằng c&ocirc;ng nghệ 3D. V&agrave; một người đ&agrave;n &ocirc;ng sẽ kể c&acirc;u chuy&ecirc;̣n về cha anh ta bằng một ứng dụng nền t&ecirc;n l&agrave; Twitter để n&oacute;i về những thứ tệ hại m&agrave; cha anh ta l&agrave;m." href="javascript:void(0)">And things got a lot more fun when the Internet came around. (Laughter) Because, not only could people broadcast their stories throughout the world, but they could do so using what seemed to be an infinite amount of devices.&nbsp;For example, one company would tell a story of love through its very own search engine. One Taiwanese production studio would interpret American politics in 3D. (Laughter)&nbsp;And one man would tell the stories of his father by using a platform called Twitter to communicate the excrement his father would gesticulate.</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Sau tất cả những điều n&agrave;y, mọi người dừng lại; nh&igrave;n lại ph&iacute;a sau. Họ nhận ra rằng, trong 6.000 năm của việc kể chuy&ecirc;̣n, họ đ&atilde; đi từ vẽ h&igrave;nh săn bắn l&ecirc;n v&aacute;ch hang động đến tả lại Shakespeare tr&ecirc;n trang Facebook. Đ&oacute; l&agrave; l&yacute; do để ch&uacute;c mừng. Nghệ thuật kể chuy&ecirc;̣n vẫn kh&ocirc;ng thay đổi. V&agrave; phần lớn l&agrave;, c&aacute;c c&acirc;u chuy&ecirc;̣n được t&aacute;i sinh. Nhưng c&aacute;ch m&agrave; người ta kể chuy&ecirc;̣n đ&atilde; lu&ocirc;n ph&aacute;t triển với sự thuần khiết v&agrave; mới lạ kh&ocirc;ng ngừng." href="javascript:void(0)">And after all this, everyone paused; they took a step back. They realized that, in 6,000 years of storytelling, they''ve gone from depicting hunting on cave walls to depicting Shakespeare on Facebook walls.&nbsp;And this was a cause for celebration. The art of storytelling has remained unchanged. And for the most part, the stories are recycled. But the way that humans tell the stories has always evolved with pure, consistent novelty.</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="V&agrave; họ nhớ về một người, một người Đức tuyệt vời, mỗi khi một thiết bị kể chuy&ecirc;̣n mới được ra l&ograve;. V&agrave; v&igrave; thế, những kh&aacute;n giả -- những người đ&aacute;ng y&ecirc;u v&agrave; xinh đẹp -- m&atilde;i m&atilde;i sống hạnh ph&uacute;c." href="javascript:void(0)"><span>And they remembered a man, one amazing German, every time a new storytelling device popped up next. And for that, the audience -- the lovely, beautiful audience -- would live happily ever after. (Applause)</span></a></p>\r\n</div>', '');
